    <p style="font-family:Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size:170%;"><b>ABOUT CHICKEN BIRYANI</b></p>
    <p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:130%;">Chicken Biryani is a delightful dish that combines tender chicken, fragrant basmati rice, and a symphony of spices. Originating from the Indian subcontinent, this flavorful meal is cherished for its rich taste and aromatic appeal. The blend of cumin, coriander, cardamom, and cinnamon creates a tantalizing experience. Layers of marinated chicken and rice meld during slow cooking, resulting in a mouthwatering masterpiece.</p>
